The walk from that building to the lobby is about 2-3 minutes.	The hotel is conveniently located, just across the street from the airport entrance with a free shuttle that runs every 20 minutes.	Our room was connected to the main lobby by a skyway; we were in building 5 -- it wasn't very close.	It is on a busy street and I didn't see a restaurant within walking distance so I ate in the lobby.	I can walk down to the lobby and get free wifi or use their computers for no charge.